---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Data" description="No datasets published yet — first experiment in progress. Data released after peer review.">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-24">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 mb-2">
      Data
    </h1>
    <p class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 mb-10">
      All experiment data is open, immutable, and version-controlled. MIT licensed.
      Datasets are published only after peer review confirms integrity.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <!-- No published datasets yet -->
      <div class="border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800 rounded-lg p-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400 mb-4">
          No datasets published yet. The first experiment is in progress.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/misty-step/laboratory"
          class="text-sm text-amber-500 hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Browse repository on GitHub &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- R7 live data — valid, not yet formally published -->
      <div class="border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">
            Round 7 — Live Data
          </h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-mono bg-stone-100 dark:bg-stone-800 text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">
            valid, unpublished
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 mb-4">
          N=1,200 live API trials, 9 models, 5 defense conditions, direct injection channel.
          Data is real; formal publication pending next experiment design.
        </p>
        <dl class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-sm mb-4">
          <dt class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400">Format</dt>
          <dd class="text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 font-mono">CSV</dd>
          <dt class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400">Rows</dt>
          <dd class="text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 font-mono">1,200</dd>
          <dt class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400">Mode</dt>
          <dd class="text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 font-mono">live (real API calls)</dd>
          <dt class="text-stone-500 dark:text-stone-400">Models</dt>
          <dd class="text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100">9 across 5 providers</dd>
        </dl>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/misty-step/laboratory/tree/master/experiments/prompt-injection-boundary-tags/rounds/round7/data"
          class="text-sm text-amber-500 hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Browse on GitHub &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Reproducibility -->
      <div class="border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-stone-900 dark:text-stone-100 mb-3">
          Reproducibility
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-400 mb-4">
          Harnesses include a deterministic simulation mode (seeded RNG, no API keys) for
          local development and testing. Simulation data is never published as findings.
        </p>
        <pre class="bg-stone-900 text-stone-100 p-4 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono overflow-x-auto"><code>git clone https://github.com/misty-step/laboratory.git
cd laboratory
python3 -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e .
make run-r7     # simulation (no API keys needed)
make analyze-r7 # produces report/</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
